<https://w3id.org/ssbd/attributed> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Agent> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Agent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/attributed> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/attributed> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an agent to an entity via an activity that both the agent and entity participates to."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/attributed> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "attributed"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/attributed> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The activity is through overlapped by the agent and overcrossed by the entity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/attributed> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "There may or may not be a causal interaction between the agent and entity."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/causal
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causal> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causal> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The root of all causal SSbD relations."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causal> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "causal"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causal> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Causality is the fundamental concept describing how entities affect each other."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/causedBy
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasInfluencedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/causal> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A relation between an entity that causally affects the subject."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "John yesterday is the cause of John today, is an example of temporal-like causality. The desk supporting my laptop is a space-like causality."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/causedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "causedBy"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/chemicalClass
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/chemicalClass> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/chemicalClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/standsFor> .
