# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an activity to an entity that is input to the activity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasInput"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The activity A proper overlaps the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E causes A."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasJunctionPart
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasJunctionPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasJunctionPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasJunctionPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasJunctionPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasJunctionPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "hasSpatioTemporalPart"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasJunctionPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The part is connected with the rest item or members with both hasNext (or its inverse) and hasContact relations."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasJunctionPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasJunctionPart"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasMeasurementUnit
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasMeasurementUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasMeasurementUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasDescription> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasMeasurementUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/Property> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasMeasurementUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Connects a property to its unit."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasMeasurementUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasUnit"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasMeasurementUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "`ssbd:hasMeasurementUnit` is intended to refer to a unit in an existing unit ontology, like QUDT or EMMO."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an activity to an entity that is the output of the activity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasOutput"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The activity A proper overlaps the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E is caused by A."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/overlaps> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ReflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The primitive relation that express the concept of an entity being part of another one."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasPart"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "OWL2 does not allow non-simple (e.g. transitive) properties to appear in disjoint property axioms. We therefore implement the transitivity of hasPart using SWRL rules instead of asserting it with owl:TransitiveProperty."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasParticipant
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between a process and an object participating to it, i.e. that is relevant to the process itself."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasParticipant"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Participation is a parthood relation - you must be part of the process to contribute to it. A participant whose 4D extension is totally contained within the process."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasPart> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between an entity and one of its parts, when both entities are distinct."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasProperPart"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperty
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/isRepresentedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/Property> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Connects a thing to one of its properties."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasProperty"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSoftware
