<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/Computation> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/Software> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "hasSoftwareAgent"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates a computation to the software used to perform the computation."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasSoftware"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSpatialPart
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A proper part of a whole, whose parts always cover the full temporal extension of the whole within a spatial interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasSpatialPart"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The part is connected with the rest item or members with hasContact relations only (no hasNext)."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/Process> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/Process> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between a process and one of its process parts."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasSubProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasSubProcess"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasTemporalPart
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasProperPart> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A relation that identify a proper item part of the whole, whose parts always cover the full spatial extension of the whole within a time interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasTemporalPart"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "A temporal part of an item cannot both cause and be caused by any other proper part of the item."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ssbd/implementsModel
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/implementsModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/implementsModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/standsFor> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/implementsModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/implementsModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/implementsModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/Software> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/implementsModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/Model> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/implementsModel> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates a software to the model it implements."@en .
