<https://w3id.org/ssbd/standsFor> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Connects a sign (e.g. a property) to an entity (a 'referent')."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/standsFor> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "standsFor"@en .
