<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ssbd/hasInput> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an activity to an entity that it used."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "For example, :baking :used :spoon, :egg, :oven ." .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "used"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ssbd/used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The activity A proper overlaps the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E causes A."@en .
